---
import SiteLayout from "../../layouts/SiteLayout.astro";
import { site } from "../../lib/site";
---

<SiteLayout title="About">
	<section class="mt-2">
		<h1>About</h1>
		<div class="mt-6 max-w-2xl rounded-2xl border border-zinc-200/80 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
			<div class="prose max-w-none">
				<p>
					I’m a mathematics student at {site.affiliation} and an undergraduate researcher. My interests include
					<strong> algebraic coding theory</strong>, <strong>algebraic geometry</strong>, and <strong>cryptography</strong>.
				</p>

				<h2>Research</h2>
				<p>
					I’m especially interested in problems where algebraic structure leads to efficient algorithms or concrete constructions
					(e.g., error-correcting codes and post-quantum security). For a snapshot, see <a href="/research/">Research</a> and
					<a href="/publications/">Publications</a>.
				</p>

				<h2>Current activities</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>Undergraduate research with <a href="https://www2.tulane.edu/~mcan/">Mahir Bilen Can</a></li>
					<li>Coursework and seminars in pure and applied mathematics</li>
					<li>Reproducible computational workflows (Python/R/LaTeX)</li>
				</ul>

				<h2>Links & contact</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>
						CV: <a href="/ENCV.pdf">PDF</a> or <a href="/cv/">web version</a>
					</li>
					<li>Email: <a href={`mailto:${site.email}`}>{site.email}</a></li>
					<li>GitHub: <a href={site.social.github}>@elinaig</a></li>
					<li>LinkedIn: <a href={site.social.linkedin}>eli-naig</a></li>
					<li>ORCID: <a href={site.social.orcid}>0009-0003-9324-2382</a></li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</SiteLayout>
